data.description: HEART OF MELBOURNE BEACH! This spacious 2,420 sf 3/2 home is within walking distance of the beach and is near shopping, churches, schools, and a fantastic golf course. Style, comfort, and luxury throughout with tiled floors, updated kitchen, enormous primary bedroom suite w/large walk-in closet, large formal living room and dining room with crown molding, and an inviting family room with wood burning fireplace and full masonry wall. Includes dual climate system, custom cabinetry in the breakfast area, and a large garage with a full wall of storage cabinetry. Sliding glass doors open to a bonus room perfect for billiards, ping pong, or a multitude of family activities and a large utility room. This beautifully landscaped retreat has a large, fenced backyard with abundant room for a pool.
